  <lyrics>[V1]
 Jesucristo wicharipunampaj
 Jatun kamachiyta saqewarqanchej.
 
[C]
 /Evangeliomanta parlamunanchejpaj
 Diospa atiyninwan sapa ujninchej./
 
[V2]
 Dios Tatanchej nishan: "Sapa p’unchay
 Palabrayta willay tukuy runasman."
 
[V3]
 Pichus creej Jesuspa sutimpi
 Paymin salvo kanqa ñak'ariy manta.
 
[V4]
 Jesucristo phuyuspi riporqa,
 Ajinallatataj urayk'amonqa.
 
[V5]
 Jesús nerqa wakichimunanta
 Ashkha tiyanasta janaj pachapi.
 
</lyrics></song>